://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 21st Century\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"All TimeThe 500 Greatest Albums\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"Time100\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21st Century Rolling Stonedug\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"theInternational Olympic Committeeand\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She discussed her personal path as an athlete, the importance of women's sports in Afghanistan, the governance of the Games, and life for women under the Taliban.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her personal path\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the governance\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have had an interesting path to the Olympic world.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interesting path\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic world\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your family fled Afghanistan in 1994 - the year you were born - to escape conflict and instability as the Taliban gained prominence.\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your family\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"instability\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"prominence\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You wound up in Iran, where you began playing sports as a kid, correct?Yes, when I was in Iran, I went to martial arts, kung fu classes.\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9515664846044413, \"rank\": 0.05089175542031647, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}, {\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma_ray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0603716262114065e-26, \"text\": \"Yes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma_ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma_ray\"}, {\"begin\": 2803, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9515664846044413, \"rank\": 0.05089175542031647, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"martial arts\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"kung fu classes\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I started with aquatic swimming when I was five years old.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aquatic swimming\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did soccer, skateboarding, many sports.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"many sports\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your parents encouraged you to pursue sports?Yes, yes.\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your parents\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2973}, {\"ngram\": \"sports?Yes\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I grew up with three boys, so I was always playing with them.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three boys\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And my father, he used to be a coach in Taekwondo in Afghanistan.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3118, \"end\": 3127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4251595000257875e-25, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}, {\"begin\": 3131, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When my parents left the country, it was not safe anymore; there was a lot of discrimination against different ethnicities, restrictions that both women and men were facing.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"different ethnicities\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"restrictions\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"both women\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3296}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We became refugees.\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"refugees\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your family later returned to Afghanistan, after the Taliban had been toppled by U.S.-led forces.\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3369, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your family\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.-led forces\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That must have been a strange experience as a young girl.We returned from Iran in 2003, when I was nine years old.\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3511, \"end\": 3515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9515664846044413, \"rank\": 0.05089175542031647, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strange experience\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"a young girl\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went from, I would say, from heaven to hell.\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagine that you are in a battlefield: all destroyed buildings and no clean water.\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a battlefield\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"no clean water\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pollution, poverty, dry weather, no trees, nothing.\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pollution, poverty\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3700}, {\"ngram\": \"dry weather\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"no trees\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3723}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not even one single swimming pool.\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not even one single swimming pool\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing.\", \"from\": 37