le\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ContentWhere\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3811}, {\"ngram\": \"Stream\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3821}, {\"ngram\": \"Miami\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"Cable\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"FreeWhere\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4035}, {\"ngram\": \"an Official Team USA World Cup Soccer Jersey Online\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4094}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4108}, {\"ngram\": \"public\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4208}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4289}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4299}, {\"ngram\": \"a stigma\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women would not dare to wear sneakers or to carry a backpack even, because in the last few years, Afghanistan was run by Taliban, so schools were closed.\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 4466, \"end\": 4473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"sneakers\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4382}, {\"ngram\": \"a backpack\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4441}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women still wore the burka; the Taliban was not there, but still women were wearing it because it became a norm.\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4531, \"end\": 4538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"the burka\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4569}, {\"ngram\": \"a norm\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you face backlash for stepping out in your sneakers?Of course, we would hear bad words, insults from men, young boys.\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4660, \"end\": 4668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sneakers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.014982662128063e-19, \"text\": \"sneakers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sneakers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sneakers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"bad words\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"insults\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4721}, {\"ngram\": \"young boys\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They would harass us.\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I knew that it's up to us, the young generation, to change, and it requires all this emotional and psychological energy.\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4786}, {\"ngram\": \"the young generation\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"all this emotional and psychological energy\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the sneakers and with the backpack and my school uniform, when I walked in the streets in Kabul, I tried, in my brain, to say to myself, \\\"Samira, as a young girl in Afghanistan, you should normalize this.\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 5091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4977, \"end\": 4982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.753848773388265e-17, \"text\": \"Kabul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\"}, {\"begin\": 5025, \"end\": 5031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/League_of_Legends\", \"score\": 0.9999999996298357, \"rank\": 3.702712343879206e-10, \"text\": \"Samira\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/League_of_Legends\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/League_of_Legends\"}, {\"begin\": 5052, \"end\": 5063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sneakers\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4899}, {\"ngram\": \"the backpack\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4921}, {\"ngram\": \"my school uniform\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4943}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4973}, {\"ngram\": \"my brain\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5004}, {\"ngram\": \"a young girl\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shock for the population, but you should normalize it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5092, \"to\": 5154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shock\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5104}, {\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I started biking on a dusty street, not on the main road, but on my home street.\", \"from\": 5155, \"to\": 5235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dusty street\", \"from\": 5175, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"the main road\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5211}, {\"ngram\": \"my home street\", \"from\": 5220, \"to\": 5234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an individual, I started advocating this way.\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an individual\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That takes a lot of courage to go against adults who are saying, \\\"You can not do this.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5297, \"to\": 5302}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5313}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Uneducated adults - people who did not know how to speak to a woman or how to treat a woman or a young girl.\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Uneducated adults\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5390}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5399}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5440}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5457, \"to\": 5464}, {\"ngram\": \"a young girl\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to emphasize that women in Afghanistan and their advocates, they have psychological issues from all of this; for instance, for us athletes, we were fighting in two places: competing on the field of play, and also off the court in society, on cobble streets, fighting for our rights.\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5516, \"end\": 5527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that women\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5512}, {\"ngram\": \"their advocates\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5547}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological issues\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5579}, {\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5610}, {\"ngram\": \"us athletes\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"two places\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5659}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5683}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5691}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 5706, \"to\": 5715}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 5719, \"to\": 5726}, {\"ngram\": \"cobble streets\", \"from\": 5731, \"to\": 5745}, {\"ngram\": \"our rights\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I hear from Afghan women that this is Afghan culture, or this is Islamic culture, and I say that's not our culture, that's not what Islam says.\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5795, \"end\": 5801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999326974, \"rank\": 6.774007753929325e-11, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 5821, \"end\": 5835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afghan culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 5848, \"end\": 5863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_culture\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Islamic culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_culture\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our culture\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5897}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 5915, \"to\": 5920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Islam says that the right for education is for men and women.\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 5988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 5932}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 5952}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5966}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5977}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5982, \"to\": 5987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about religion, it's about the norm that you create in your society.\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 6066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 6004, \"to\": 6012}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 6025, \"to\": 6033}, {\"ngram\": \"your society\", \"from\": 6053, \"to\": 6065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People establish the norm.\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 6067, \"to\": 6073}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 6084, \"to\": 6092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted as an individual to normalize something else, which is sport and education.\", \"from\": 6094, \"to\": 6178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an individual\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6119}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6133, \"to\": 6142}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6163}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 6168, \"to\": 6177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You fell in love with basketball, eventually becoming captain of the national team, and your march to the International Olympic Committee began.Yes, I started playing for the youth national team in 2009.\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6286, \"end\": 6317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6196}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 6202, \"to\": 6212}, {\"ngram\": \"captain\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6241}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 6245, \"to\": 6262}, {\"ngram\": \"your march\", \"from\": 6268, \"to\": 6278}, {\"ngram\": \"the youth national team\", \"from\": 6351, \"to\": 6374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few years later, when I was 18, my birthday gift from my coach was that he added me to the adult team.\", \"from\": 6384, \"to\": 6488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my birthday gift\", \"from\": 6418, \"to\": 6434}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 6440, \"to\": 6448}, {\"ngram\": \"the adult team\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2011, I became a member of the Afghan National Olympic Committee, and then the International Olympic Committee in 2018.\", \"from\": 6489, \"to\": 6611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6523, \"end\": 6556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afghan National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan_National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan_National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 6571, \"end\": 6602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I played basketball until the Taliban came in 2021.\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 6663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6642, \"end\": 6649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 6621, \"to\": 6631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where were you when the Taliban seized power?I was pursuing my master's degree in advanced studies in sport administration and technology in Switzerland.\", \"from\": 6665, \"to\": 6818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6689, \"end\": 6696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999991025583247, \"rank\": 8.974422970819794e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}, {\"begin\": 6806, \"end\": 6817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.07840806211192e-13, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"power?I\", \"from\": 6704, \"to\": 6711}, {\"ngram\": \"my master's degree\", \"from\": 6725, \"to\": 6743}, {\"ngram\": \"advanced studies\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6763}, {\"ngram\": \"sport administration\", \"from\": 6767, \"to\": 6787}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It must have been devastating to see the news.I saw videos of Taliban with their guns in the middle of downtown in Kabul.\", \"from\": 6820, \"to\": 6941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6882, \"end\"