orking all the time.\", \"from\": 7985, \"to\": 8030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also had to perform as an IOC member, which is a great responsibility.\", \"from\": 8031, \"to\": 8103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8059, \"end\": 8069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC member\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great responsibility\", \"from\": 8080, \"to\": 8102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And my family needed to leave the country too; they went from Afghanistan to Iran, from Iran to Turkey, and now they are in France.\", \"from\": 8104, \"to\": 8235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8166, \"end\": 8177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9361858381378713, \"rank\": 0.06816398973665337, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 8181, \"end\": 8185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9515664846044413, \"rank\": 0.05089175542031647, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}, {\"begin\": 8192, \"end\": 8196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9515664846044413, \"rank\": 0.05089175542031647, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}, {\"begin\": 8200, \"end\": 8206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999980068898221, \"rank\": 1.993111473541117e-06, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia