"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 8497, \"to\": 8502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You see that all countries are promoting sport, and then I see my country.\", \"from\": 8504, \"to\": 8578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all countries\", \"from\": 8517, \"to\": 8530}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 8545, \"to\": 8550}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 8567, \"to\": 8577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic teams must include both women and men.\", \"from\": 8580, \"to\": 8626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic teams\", \"from\": 8580, \"to\": 8593}, {\"ngram\": \"both women\", \"from\": 8607, \"to\": 8617}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 8622, \"to\": 8625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did officials pull together a gender-equal team of Afghan athletes to represent the country?Olympic athletes are always chosen by national sports federations - the governing bodies for various sports in each country, such as USA Gymnastics, for instance.\", \"from\": 8627, \"to\": 8885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8682, \"end\": 8688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999326974, \"rank\": 6.774007753929325e-11, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 8856, \"end\": 8870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999995689841873, \"rank\": 4.3101615621362757e-07, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 8635, \"to\": 8644}, {\"ngram\": \"a gender-equal team\", \"from\": 8659, \"to\": 8678}, {\"ngram\": \"the country?Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 8711, \"to\": 8739}, {\"ngram\": \"national sports federations\", \"from\": 8761, \"to\": 8788}, {\"ngram\": \